-- EFG Names Pernollet as Chief Financial Officer, Replacing Van Den Steen
-- Warren Giles
-- 2010-07-28T05:13:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/efg-names-pernollet-as-chief-financial-officer-replacing-van-den-steen.html

          
          
             EFG International AG said Chief
Executive Officer Rudy van den Steen will step down, effective
Oct. 1, and will be replaced by Jean-Christophe Pernollet.  
          
          


  


        